    },
    {
      "point": "Significant limitation: strong dependency on model scale without explanation",
      "evidence": "Instruction tuning benefits *only* emerged with sufficient model scale (100B+ models), with smaller models degrading. The paper offers no theoretical hypotheses or deeper insights into *why* this scale dependency exists, limiting understanding and broader applicability."
